channel.title: Welcome from Ziheng Zhang!

item.description: Ziheng Zhang is a master student at the School of Information Science and Techology, ShanghaiTech University. His research insterests include computer vision and deep learning. Before coming to ShanghaiTech University, he receives his BSc. Degree from Xidian University, Xi`An, China.
